**Last updated:** 09/aug/2028

Welcome to the cool-finds app. By using this app, you agree to the following terms:

## 1. Use of the App

- The cool-finds app allows you to post videos programmatically to your TikTok account and retrieve basic video analytics via TikTok’s API.
